                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-249-defend1820 t18310908-249-punish1279"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>F. ROPER - <rs id="t18310908-249-verdict1280" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-249-verdict1280" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
